# Rust
target/
target_*/
# Side `CARGO_TARGET_DIR=*` trees (mostly repo root); global `target-*/` also covers nested mistakes.
target-*/
.cargo-targets/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock

# Node
**/node_modules/
**/out/
node_modules/
dist/
dist1/
docs-astro/src/content/docs
docs-astro/public/assets
docs-astro/public/.well-known
.env

# Local TOESTUB / audit outputs (do not commit large JSON baselines)
/artifacts/

# === SCRATCH / EPHEMERAL / LOGS ===
scratch/*
!scratch/.gitkeep
test_output*.txt
bundle_*.txt
*.log


